Attorney Alexander Paul Seifert in court for State of Wisconsin. Attorney Halyburton updates the court, has received the complaint and went over it with her client, would like a PH, asks to be heard on bond and makes that argument, asking for signature bond or low cash bond ($500), does not object to any non-monetary conditions. State objects to reduction of bond, realizes it will take awhile as it is OWI 5th & 6th - drug related - results are taking 6-8 months, unable to see the 4th as it is a new case in another county. Court has considered all statements and bond factors, will continue bond as set for reasons as indicated on the record. Halyburton would like PH within time limits. Court has PH scheduled.
